<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Gareth Bale was seen sporting a big smile as he arrived at Tottenham's Enfield training ground to sign the contract to seal his return to his former side.Â </p>

<p>Sportsmail exclusively revealed on Wednesday that Bale has agreed a season-long loan deal to return to north London.</p>

<p>He will earn more than Â£13million in wages as part of the one-year deal negotiated by Tottenham chairman Levy.Â  After flying into Luton airport shortly after midday on Friday, he was driven to the club's training base and was greeted by excitable supporters giving him a hero's welcome.</p>

<p>Gareth Bale gave a thumbs up to supporters as he was driven into Tottenham's training groundÂ </p>

